  "llm_summary": "The chatbot starts with a Kodexo Labs welcome menu. Most discovery-focused options route the user into a service selector. After the user chooses a service, the bot asks for a project brief, then uses an AI Agent state called READY_KL before collecting timeline and budget. It then collects name, email, phone, and referral source. Finally, it confirms that the team will respond within 24 hours and gives the user a choice to schedule a call or wait for email. Both final paths submit to a webhook and end with a goodbye message. The chatbot also has separate shortcut branches for booking a free consultation and viewing contact/location information."
